reviewText: One of the best little-known films.  Saw it on tv many years ago and have looked for a personal copy.  Ricardo Montalban was terrific as the detective, and it's a shame that he didn't have the opportunity for more roles like this.

Enjoyed it very much. A great mystery story and fine detective work for that time. Well acted.
I had to buy this movie again as the other 2 movie set failed and others in the Film Noir Vol. 4 set from Warner.
I had a double set and the film Mystery Street went  bad so I had to order this single.  Love the movie.
This movie was a great murder mystery.  The action was fast paced, and the story quite interesting.
Great movie and transaction. Thank you!
I feel this DVD is of very good quality as a classic movie fan I must recommend this DVD to all classic movie lovers I am certain you will not be disappointed at all!
